Class Projectile

java.lang.Object
com.arena.dual_arena.models.projectiles.Projectile
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bullet, GuidedRocket, ReversedBullet, ReversedRocket, Rocket
public abstract class Projectile extends Object
Abstract class representing the base functionality of a projectile in the game. Defines common properties such as range, speed, knockback, and explosion characteristics.

  • Constructor Details

    • Projectile

      protected Projectile(float speed, float knockback)
      Constructs a projectile with specified speed and knockback, without explosion modifiers.
      Parameters:
      speed - Speed at which the projectile travels.
      knockback - Knockback force the projectile imparts on hitting a target.

    • Projectile

      protected Projectile(float range, float speed, float knockback, float explosionRadiusMultiplier, float explosionKnockbackFalloff)
      Constructs a projectile with specified range, speed, knockback, and explosion characteristics.
      Parameters:
      range - Maximum distance the projectile can travel before dissipating.
      speed - Speed at which the projectile travels.
      knockback - Knockback force the projectile imparts on hitting a target.
      explosionRadiusMultiplier - Multiplier for the explosion radius.
      explosionKnockbackFalloff - Rate at which the explosion's knockback effect decreases with distance.
